    {
      "id": "cell-md-6",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Step 6: Create Derived Column \u2014 `total_amount = price \u00d7 quantity`\n\n*Note: This dataset has `initial_price` and `discount`. We'll simulate quantity = 1 as dataset has no quantity column, and also compute `discounted_amount = initial_price \u00d7 (discount / 100)`.*",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "cell-code-6",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "# Assign a default quantity of 1 (as dataset has no quantity column)\ndf['quantity'] = 1\n\n# total_amount = initial_price * quantity  (as per assignment formula)\ndf['total_amount'] = df['initial_price'] * df['quantity']\n\n# Bonus: also compute actual discount amount\ndf['discount_amount'] = df['initial_price'] * (df['discount'] / 100)\ndf['discount_amount'] = df['discount_amount'].round(2)\n\nprint('=== NEW DERIVED COLUMNS ===')\nprint(df[['title', 'initial_price', 'quantity', 'total_amount', 'discount', 'discount_amount']].head(5))",
      "metadata": {
        "trusted": true
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": "=== NEW DERIVED COLUMNS ===\n            title  initial_price  quantity  total_amount  discount  \\\n0     Lino Perros           3995         1          3995      58.0   \n1  Tommy Hilfiger           2899         1          2899      35.0   \n2           Lavie           2999         1          2999      65.0   \n3          F Gear           1675         1          1675      52.0   \n4       MYTRIDENT           2899         1          2899      17.0   \n\n   discount_amount  \n0          2317.10  \n1          1014.65  \n2          1949.35  \n3           871.00  \n4           492.83  \n"
        }
      ],
      "execution_count": 13
    },
    {
